<Layout title='Plasterers & Painters in Stoke Poges | Hancock' description='Plastering and painting in Stoke Poges. Fixed-price quotes from City & Guilds certified contractors covering Stoke Poges and the surrounding area.' activePage='areas'>
<section style="position:relative;height:340px;display:flex;align-items:flex-end;">
  <div style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;bottom:0;background-image:url('/uploads/Hancock-plastering-and-painting%20(3).webp');background-size:cover;background-position:center 40%;"></div>
  <div style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;bottom:0;background:linear-gradient(to top,rgba(15,23,42,0.9) 0%,rgba(15,23,42,0.45) 60%,rgba(15,23,42,0.15) 100%);"></div>
  <div style="position:relative;z-index:1;max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 24px 48px;width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;">
    <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);margin:0 0 12px;"><a href="/" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);text-decoration:none;">Home</a> / <a href="/areas" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);text-decoration:none;">Areas</a> / Stoke Poges</p>
    <h1 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(30px,5vw,52px);font-weight:700;color:#ffffff;margin:0 0 10px;letter-spacing:-0.04em;line-height:1.05;">Plasterer in Stoke Poges</h1>
    <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.75);margin:0;">SL2 · Plastering, rendering &amp; decorating across Stoke Poges and Farnham Common.</p>
  </div>
</section>
<section style="padding:56px 24px;background:#ffffff;border-bottom:1px solid #E2E8F0;">
  <div style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;">
    <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#11ADE2;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 12px;">About Stoke Poges</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(20px,3vw,30px);font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 18px;letter-spacing:-0.03em;line-height:1.2;">Village and executive residential between Slough and Beaconsfield — a mix of period and modern properties with consistent plastering and decorating demand.</h2>
    <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 14px;">Stoke Poges sits in the Buckinghamshire Green Belt between Slough and Beaconsfield. The village has a historic churchyard character with period properties on its lanes. Surrounding roads have 1950s–70s detached and executive newer builds. Exterior painting and rendering are the primary external jobs. Interior plastering and skimming during renovation are consistent domestic work.</p>
  </div>
</section>
<section style="padding:56px 24px;background:#F8FAFC;border-bottom:1px solid #E2E8F0;">
  <div style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;">
    <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#11ADE2;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 12px;">Common problems</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(20px,3vw,28px);font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 28px;letter-spacing:-0.03em;">What goes wrong in Stoke Poges's housing stock.</h2>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(240px,1fr));gap:20px;">
      <div style="background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;border-radius:8px;padding:24px;"><h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 8px;">Render on detached homes</h3><p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">The 1950s–70s detached and executive stock often carries rendered elevations that weather and discolour, needing patch repair and a fresh masonry paint system.</p></div>
      <div style="background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;border-radius:8px;padding:24px;"><h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 8px;">Period fabric in the village</h3><p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">The historic village core around the churchyard has period properties with solid walls and lime plaster needing sympathetic, breathable repair.</p></div>
      <div style="background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;border-radius:8px;padding:24px;"><h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 8px;">Refit and extension re-skims</h3><p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">Renovation work on the larger homes leaves walls that need plastering out and re-skimming to a flat, paint-ready finish.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section style="padding:56px 24px;background:#ffffff;border-bottom:1px solid #E2E8F0;">
  <div style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;">
    <div style="display:flex;gap:64px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:48px;">
      <div style="flex:1;min-width:300px;">
        <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#11ADE2;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 12px;">Neighbourhoods we work in</p>
        <h2 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(20px,3vw,28px);font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 18px;letter-spacing:-0.03em;line-height:1.2;">Green Belt village and executive residential.</h2>
        <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 14px;">Stoke Poges sits in the Buckinghamshire Green Belt between Slough and Beaconsfield, famous for the churchyard that inspired Gray's <em>Elegy</em>. The village has a historic core with period properties on its lanes; the surrounding roads, toward <strong>Farnham Common</strong>, hold 1950s–70s detached and newer executive housing on generous plots.</p>
        <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0;">It's an affluent, semi-rural area with consistent plastering and decorating demand across both the period and modern stock.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="flex:1;min-width:300px;">
        <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#11ADE2;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 12px;">What homeowners ask for</p>
        <h2 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(20px,3vw,28px);font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 18px;letter-spacing:-0.03em;line-height:1.2;">Rendering, painting, and skimming.</h2>
        <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 14px;">Exterior render and masonry painting are the primary external jobs; interior plastering, skimming, and decorating during renovation are the consistent domestic work. Period repair features in the village core. Exterior work is scheduled for dry conditions.</p>
        <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0;">Considered budgets, careful work, fixed price up front.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#11ADE2;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 24px;">Working in Stoke Poges</p>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr));gap:20px;">
      <div><h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 8px;">~20 minutes from base</h3><p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">A clear run from Harefield via Denham and the A412. Covered on planned runs with Burnham and Iver.</p></div>
      <div><h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 8px;">Render &amp; exterior ready</h3><p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">Set up for full render repair and masonry painting on the detached stock, with the right access equipment.</p></div>
      <div><h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 8px;">Easy access</h3><p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">Generous plots and driveways give ample room for the van, materials, and scaffolding where needed.</p></div>
      <div><h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 8px;">Clean, tidy, insured</h3><p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">Surfaces protected, site left tidy daily. Fully insured, City &amp; Guilds qualified, no subcontractors.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
